I"a<p>I am trying to write small microservice benchmark for java, lately java microservice framework are popping up from every corner :smile: actually it is becoming little bit annoying, java world becoming js world.</p>

<p>Anyway while writing some test I start getting the error below</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">Internal Server Error
